      * GP Global Menu Item Text
     FGPMTXTPD  IF   E             DISK    PREFIX(A_)
     F                                     INFSR(*PSSR)

      * SF Zonal Menu Action Codes by Unique Code
     FSFMENUJ0  IF   E           K DISK    PREFIX(B_)
     F                                     INFSR(*PSSR)

      * Zonal Extract File for List View
     FSFMNUEXPD O    E             DISK    USROPN
     F                                     INFSR(*PSSR)

